expo and conferences, praising the seamless organization, impactful discussions, and opportunities for collaboration. The event successfully connected ministries, industry leaders, innovators, and end users, driving meaningful dialogue and partnerships for a sustainable future.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr indent="0" lvl="0" marL="0" rtl="0" algn="just"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="100000"/></a:lnSpc><a:spcBef><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcBef><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcAft><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:t></a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr sz="900"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr indent="0" lvl="0" marL="0" rtl="0" algn="just"><a:lnSpc><a:spcPct val="100000"/></a:lnSpc><a:spcBef><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcBef><a:spcAft><a:spcPts val="0"/></a:spcAft><a:buNone/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:rPr><a:t>Messages of gratitude poured in from participants, with many emphasizing the national importance of the event and its role in addressing critical challenges in the bioenergy ecosystem. From government dignitaries to international representatives, the appreciation underscored Bio Energy Global 2025 as a hub of innovation, knowledge exchange, and business opportunity.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><