" lang="en-US" sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:rPr><a:t>Yashobhoomi, IICC, Dwarka, New Delhi</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:rPr><a:t>. Building on the landmark success of this year, the 2026 edition will not only raise the bar for innovation, collaboration, and global partnerships but will also feature concurrent shows—</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr b="1" lang="en-US" sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:rPr><a:t>Waste To Energy, Wireeex, and Reneweex</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:rPr><a:t>. Together, these platforms will create a powerful ecosystem for advancing clean technologies, accelerating cross-sector synergies, and driving the global journey toward a sustainable, net-zero future.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr sz="1700"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="dk1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:ea typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:cs typeface="Trebuchet MS"/><a:sym typeface="Trebuchet MS"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>